{"tid":989013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德國外長馬斯反對中國武力恫嚇台灣 台灣外交部表示感謝","createTime":"2019-01-20T13:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T05:43:42.000Z","uid":48083,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ac343f1f8fdc0037ad84ca2e89c34c383ca0444b","tid":989013,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T13:59:40.000Z","msg":"台灣外交部對德國表示不接受中國以武力威脅台灣表示感謝。台灣外交部星期天說，德國外交部長馬斯(Heiko Maas)表示拒絕以武力作為解決兩岸問題的手段，並呼籲歐盟在這一問題上採取一致立場，台灣對此表示熱烈歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n中國國家主席習近平最近在中國《告台灣同胞書》發表40週年紀念會上講話時對台灣提出嚴厲警告，稱中國不承諾放棄使用武力，保留採取他所謂的「一切必要措施的選項」。<br />\n<br />\n德國議會友台小組主席威爾什(Klaus-Peter Willsch)上星期在議會的一次全會上，就習近平發出的這一威脅提出質詢，德國外交部長馬斯表示，德國一貫不接受任何以軍事威嚇作為解決爭端的做法。馬斯還說，過去中國曾對個別歐盟成員國施加壓力，阻撓歐盟就有關議題達成明確決議，他希望歐盟在台灣問題上能夠採取一致立場。<br />\n<br />\n台灣外交部還對德國議員威爾什提出這一議題表示感謝，並表示未來台灣將繼續與包括德國在內理念相近國家攜手合作，共同維持台海區域和平及穩定。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/amp/German-FM-Urges-EU-Jointely-Oppose-China-Military-Threat-Over-Taiwan-20190120/4750826.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Famp%2FGerman-FM-Urges-EU-Jointely-Oppose-China-Military-Threat-Over-Taiwan-20190120%2F4750826.html&d=TGzEPEDPiIN8VDMvbLOsO54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=fe518052\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/amp/German-FM-Urges-EU-Jointely-Oppose-China-Military-Threat-Over-Taiwan-20190120/4750826.html</a>"},{"pid":"b52a4d2f258f847e65b1bbafe0a79f8978ef4ed9","tid":989013,"uid":50457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:43:10.000Z","msg":"世界在變"},{"pid":"b17a60965c224db6f3af3546eaca564183036cd8","tid":989013,"uid":41610,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:44:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">台灣表示感謝。</span>唔知點解就係好好笑"},{"pid":"434d1b29c32f765bb1725b3f439c0d63cdf96934","tid":989013,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T18:29:07.000Z","msg":"百國聯軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00403e5f03d585e731569f8714f841e2f2bdfe0d","tid":989013,"uid":5547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T00:54:10.000Z","msg":"Germany denounced PRC for threatening China.<br />\nWorld Tension +1."},{"pid":"6bf048e11bc7c38299b503a948e9ea633973437b","tid":989013,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b52a4d2f258f847e65b1bbafe0a79f8978ef4ed9","tid":989013,"uid":50457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:43:10.000Z","msg":"世界在變"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T01:28:27.000Z","msg":"潮流也在變"},{"pid":"1165236f08059b9ba6fcaeb4502552cdfabfd4ee","tid":989013,"uid":1643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:43:42.000Z","msg":"爭在邊個帶頭同台灣建交"}]}